Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

Key assumptions:
- Docker-compose service is called `backend`

### How to create a migration

```bash
docker-compose exec backend alembic revision --autogenerate -m "migration_name"
```

### How to apply the migration

```bash
docker-compose exec backend alembic upgrade head
```

## How to undo the last migration
```bash
docker-compose exec backend alembic downgrade -1
```
Read more: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48242324/undo-last-alembic-migration


## How to downgrade to a specific migration
```bash
## View the migration history
docker-compose exec backend alembic history
# Undo migrations to a previous checkpoint
docker-compose exec backend alembic downgrade <migration_id>
```